target_assessment.type_match_reasoning: The audit reported no findings and classified the contract as safe, despite the ground truth indicating a reentrancy vulnerability in the transfer function.

notes: The contract contains a reentrancy vulnerability in the transfer function (LN-48 to LN-57). It uses a nonReentrant modifier but calls _notifyTransfer (LN-59 to LN-68) which performs an external call to a potentially malicious contract after state changes (balances[msg.sender] -= amount). This violates the Checks-Effects-Interactions pattern. The audit failed to detect this.
